data.title: 2314 Plum St, Parkersburg, WV 26101
data.meta_description: Zillow has 30 photos of this $175,500 4 beds, 2 baths, 1,800 Square Feet single family home located at 2314 Plum St, Parkersburg, WV 26101 built in 1925. MLS #5046076.
data.text: This beautifully remodeled two-story brick home is move-in ready and waiting for you! Featuring all-new electrical work, this house combines modern convenience with classic charm. Enjoy the gleaming hardwood floors throughout, providing warmth and elegance. The spacious, fenced-in backyard is perfect for outdoor activities, and relaxation. Additionally, the home includes an unfinished basement, offering plenty of storage space. Don’t miss this opportunity to own a lovely, updated home that’s ready for you to move in and make it your own. Contact us today to schedule a viewing!
